latestIgtvVideos.title: Disclaimer: This post is not about me, but my life!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Yesterday was my 25th birthday...I woke up extremely annoyed for some reason, that I myself don't know. Perhaps it was the feeling of turning 25, a realisation of how fast life is moving that irked me. In all these years, the number of people who've come and left are countless, and I mean that quite literally! All I had was my Family by my side always. One constant support, one constant best friend, one constant person, who has never failed me is my sister @jan_ice8 . A lot of you have seen her, a lot of you might recall her as my doppelganger. But she's the one who made my 25th special. Without whom I cannot even imagine my life. This is her first video ever, which she made and I couldn't resist myself to not post it. I'd have shown it to the entire world if I could. And I think I haven't thanked her enough for pretty much everything. So, thank you for existing. Thank you for just being there always. Thank you for being the best sister. I LOVE YOU❤️

Facts about me that don’t match my appearance⬇️

- I’ve stopped taking life too seriously and rather started living it more.

- I’m a fashion girlie since childhood and I got it from my mother.

- I’m a cry baby. You raise your voice and you’d see tears rolling out in seconds!

- Firm believer of god, his plans and the universe. Everything that happens and everyone you meet - is for a reason. And for that matter, what’s yours will always find you…no matter what! 

- I trust angel numbers and google their meaning every time I come across one. 

- I’m a big time procrastinator (Working on it)

- Hate corporate but love the idea of it. How it brings you out of your bubble and let you spend time with diverse people, good and bad.

- I believe in Karma. You do good, it multiplies and comes back to you. Someone did bad to you? Let it be…you’re not them. 

- Very optimistic and aspirational, in general.

- A giver & a hoarder…to an extent that I forget the limit almost every time. 

- Not very emotionally expressive but I often talk to myself and create scenarios crying in front of the mirror as if I was in a movie

- I wanted to be an actress when I was a child. I used to believe actors sing their own songs, so I need to be a good singer too

- I love hanging out with my friends but hate stepping out of the house but also love getting ready and having a good time (If that makes sense) 

I could keep going because there’s a lot more to it…did any of these come as a shock to you? 

I’d love to know which one surprised you the most!

[Facts about me, real reel, content creator, a day in my life, my life, real talk]
